/* Transliteration seed: sml/parser/parser.sml — tryAssignStmt (lines ~976–1008).
   After tryParseAssignLHS, next token is EQ or assign binop; RHS uses **parser/expr_rhs_stub_core**
   shapes (**rhs_stub_ok_with_semi** duplicated here): atom (**40** / **73**) or **40 + 40**, then **;** (15).
   **parser/expr_pratt_stub_core** — **pratt_from_atom**, **pratt_rhs_ok_with_semi7**, **pratt_rhs_ok_with_semi** (**t6=0**) duplicated; **`try_assign_*_op_pratt_rhs_stub7`** for unary **` - lit+lit*lit ;`**.
   Brackets **LBRACKET** **16** / **RBRACKET** **17** align with **`lexer/token_delim_core`**.
   Composes with assign_lhs, delim, token_op **+** = 20. */

fn tok_ident() -> i32 {
  return 73;
}

fn tok_star() -> i32 {
  return 22;
}

fn tok_assign_eq() -> i32 {
  return 19;
}

